NOW,FLEXBOX-
it is a powerful tool for creating layouts, layouts itself means that which displays , so, how it displays first which text the which text in differnt font-sizes, appear, then in which background color,in which size, which iamge shoukd be ther, iun diffetnt sizes.etc,all the content will be in recatngular box. these are called layouts.
the content which arranged in manner is called layouts.
full form of flexbox is flexible box(1-D Layout method)
the flex model, we see a box, it is a parent container called flex container, in flex container, ther are diffenrent items called flex items.also the axes, which is horizontal and vertical axes, by,default the horizontal axes is called main axes, and vertical axis is called cross axis.
now to create a flex container, in a container, mark display to flex, then the items in teh flex container will be flex ietms.see the syntax-
